TY  - JOUR
TI  - Estimating Regression Models with Multiplicative Heteroscedasticity
AU  - Harvey, A. C.
AB  - [A regression model in which the disturbances exhibit a certain type of heteroscedasticity is considered. Maximum likelihood methods of estimation are developed and compared with the two-step estimation procedure. A likelihood ratio test for heteroscedasticity is suggested.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1976
